data.description: Discover the delightful home that is just what you've been looking for! This charming residence offers 3 bedrooms, a convenient 1-car garage, large lot and a new roof under 3 years old. The interconnected living room effortlessly flows into an open kitchen and dining space. Outside, a vast backyard secluded by mature shade trees awaits. It's perfect of entertaining. There is carpet just in the bedrooms that is under 2 years old along with a 2 year old water heater, dishwasher, refrigerator, 7 year old HVAC, and updated windows throughout. This house is move in ready with all of the necessities you look for in your new home. Don't miss this one!
